To use ALSA with PulseAudio, add the following to ~/.asoundrc:

# begin ~/.asoundrc
pcm.!default {
	type pulse
}

ctl.!default {
	type pulse
}

pcm.pulse {
	type pulse
}

ctl.pulse {
	type pulse
}
# end ~/.asoundrc

===========================================================================
